(QUICK STORY): First off I can’t stress enough how much this means to me.  Without yall support & God none of this would even be possible. Last year I was broke as fuck on my last $100 sitting in my car off 59th & Thunderbird at Shells gas station thinking to myself man…I gotta work harder. I’m not living up to my full potential. I ended up filling up my gas tank & said fuck it I’m bout to go chase my dreams & never look back.

Now I live in Atlanta, dropped the ALBUM OF THE YEAR 💿, starred in a Film, & have collaborated and produced for so many artists. Pops always stressed the handwork doesn’t go unnoticed 💯. Thank y’all mane. Aye 2023 🚀 the only way is 🆙

Thank you everyone who’s been patient with me. Not gone lie, This is a very touchy subject & was very hard to speak on because I love my mama. She’s my heart & soul. We didn’t have the best relationship but now we have a bond that’s unbreakable. I hope this song & music video connect with those who doesn’t have a great relationship with their parents & hopefully give them enough courage to address some past trauma in order to patch up some healing wounds & move on. 🙏🏽#KINGDOM3
